{"tid":2348044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【離譜校規】日本學校詭異校規指定內衣顏色　女生當眾解扣被老師扯胸圍帶檢查","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T13:04:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc8ee7f664cf1c82aa5b28561605e43826f1202","tid":2348044,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"日本學校出名校風嚴謹，但近日福岡縣律師會經調查發現，福岡縣內的學校有很多不合理校規，其中大部分學校要求學生的內衣顏色指定為白色，並限制了女生胸圍的顏色，老師會定期檢查內衣和胸圍顏色，甚至叫女生當眾解開外衣扣、扯出胸圍帶檢查，被律師會批評是違反人權。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日本《富士新聞網》（FNN）及《讀賣新聞》報道，福岡縣律師會調查了縣內69間中學，其中有62間學校「禁止削Undercut髮型」、57間要求「內衣顏色指定為白色」、56間禁止修眉毛，以及50間要求學生按本身性別而穿特定制服。<br />\n<br />\n而佐賀縣律師會今年亦對當地22間中學進行調查，並訪問了4位老師與2名學生的意見。該會發現，佐賀縣有老師以目視方法檢查女學生的內衣顏色，律師稻村蓉子批評此舉明顯侵犯人權。校規原意是想學生保持純樸，但矯枉過正的校規及老師的檢查手法，卻引來反效果。<br />\n<br />\n而福岡縣律師會也引述十多名學生、家長及老師指出，學生一旦穿上不乎指定顏色的內衣，會在校內被要求脫掉。老師更會要求女學生在走廊一字排開，解開胸前校服鈕扣以檢查內衣，甚至在體育館內有男學生在場，女生都會被當眾檢查內衣。福岡縣律師會批評，這些荒謬的校規是侵犯人權。<br />\n<br />\n老師掀女生裙底檢查名牌<br />\n另有女教師透露，曾被學校要求掀起女學生的裙子內側，檢查有否縫上檢查，女教師雖覺得侵犯人權，但礙於學校要求只能照做。其他詭異校規還包括襪子長度須離地15cm、男生不准戴頸巾、冬天不准穿制服以外的保暖大衣、男女生須相隔一公尺、在校內不准擊掌等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2840000/2841755/japan_thumb_20201231_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2840000%2F2841755%2Fjapan_thumb_20201231_S_1024.jpg&h=24d283b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"862993f74ecdeb1acbd7f685ec4977435e0365a0","tid":2348044,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BV6AVmh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBV6AVmh.gif&h=c32e9059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488ed25150076bb3d22bdad9bf963a9eccf40931","tid":2348044,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝦日本妹"},{"pid":"bf9195b3af58cdaf53eb3a0daafda2f994d9e471","tid":2348044,"uid":137704,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"香港夠係"},{"pid":"fdf01e5e662e02ef74abda3146d763b0c72157dc","tid":2348044,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"我又要檢查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4aa3952acea86dfba1a99b08056b17c7f9b6663","tid":2348044,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"Av情節嚟?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bb07c16f72dc975f8327f7ec4c7121cee21a83","tid":2348044,"uid":360404,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"488ed25150076bb3d22bdad9bf963a9eccf40931","tid":2348044,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝦日本妹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"日本人不嬲好針對女性"},{"pid":"0b1750f53bd676d5ae794cb0d513ebf3a241790f","tid":2348044,"uid":334765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oeRUruE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeRUruE.gif&h=05a5cd41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2107c69057da5d617fa8e0b4d9e68c67f50fa79","tid":2348044,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"其實香港好多學校都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b419993d29e7bba1a56611977ca8e8bdb0c21bd2","tid":2348044,"uid":7828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s5vaKhk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs5vaKhk.gif&h=e679f3d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea02ac6d36dbc68f4789beb3b9ec94293d3f18b4","tid":2348044,"uid":107681,"like":0,"di